Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Invasion of Grenada
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xb2f
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 30 Oct 1983
Reagan facing serious questions over decision to invade Grenada, a member of the British Commonwealth. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less